-- OrbSpawner: Ultra-efficient, event-driven orb collection with LOD system
-- Features Slither.io-style orb fade-in/pop-up for massive FPS improvement
-- Supports thousands of orbs with minimal lag by only rendering nearby ones
-- FIXED: AI snakes can now eat orbs + NO ATTACHMENT ERRORS from death orbs

--[[ -------------------------------------------------------------------------
IMPORTANT:
• All orbs (including death orbs) MUST be standalone Parts parented to Workspace.
• NEVER parent orbs, attachments, or constraints to snake segments or heads.
• All VFX (ParticleEmitters, etc) MUST be created on temporary Parts in Workspace.
• Orbs now use LOD (Level of Detail) - only nearby orbs are fully visible
---------------------------------------------------------------------------- ]]

